{"tid":1282300,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"對衝擊立會震驚 文翠珊就香港局勢向中国領導人提關注","createTime":"2019-07-03T14:06:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T14:11:11.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"31b66e47a78202c1d466b13b703c54dc05953e8d","tid":1282300,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T14:06:51.000Z","msg":"香港修訂《逃犯條例》引發多場大規模示威，7月1日更有示威者闖入立法會大肆破壞。英國首相文翠珊在國會下議院表示，已經就香港的情況，直接向中國領導人提出關注。<br />\n<br />\n她表示，尊重《中英聯合聲明》下，香港所享有的高度自治、人權及自由，是非常重要。她提到，對於有示威者暴力衝擊立法會感到震驚，但表明知道較早前的反修例遊行是和平及合法地進行。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1536525/即時-港聞-逃犯條例-對衝擊立會震驚-文翠珊就香港局勢向中國領導人提關注\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1536525%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E5%B0%8D%E8%A1%9D%E6%93%8A%E7%AB%8B%E6%9C%83%E9%9C%87%E9%A9%9A-%E6%96%87%E7%BF%A0%E7%8F%8A%E5%B0%B1%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%B1%80%E5%8B%A2%E5%90%91%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E9%A0%98%E5%B0%8E%E4%BA%BA%E6%8F%90%E9%97%9C%E6%B3%A8&d=3FtZuWe%2BwKi7N9uEGSTnHkbB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=78cb6867\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1536525%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E5%B0%8D%E8%A1%9D%E6%93%8A%E7%AB%8B%E6%9C%83%E9%9C%87%E9%A9%9A-%E6%96%87%E7%BF%A0%E7%8F%8A%E5%B0%B1%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%B1%80%E5%8B%A2%E5%90%91%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E9%A0%98%E5%B0%8E%E4%BA%BA%E6%8F%90%E9%97%9C%E6%B3%A8&h=94117be6\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1536525/即時-港聞-逃犯條例-對衝擊立會震驚-文翠珊就香港局勢向中國領導人提關注</a>"},{"pid":"af2dc80ec70b975f107c926c7445cbcd3c1e96a1","tid":1282300,"uid":167634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T14:11:11.000Z","msg":"［文宣戰對準台灣］蔡英文要做多d助攻<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1282101\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1282101</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}